videos.description: Nikola Jokic grabs the ball after the bucket and throws a full-court pass on a dime to Gary Harris for a layup.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Jokic throws full-court heave to Harris for the layup) 2020/12/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jokic throws full-court heave to Harris for the layup

videos.description: Jamal Murray whips the pass into the lane and Nikola Jokic makes the sweet one-handed catch for the bucket.

videos.headline: Curry gets the steal and 3

videos.description: Nikola Jokic hauls in the rebound and flings the one-handed pass on point to Gary Harris for the easy layup.

videos.description: Nikola Jokic gets off to a hot start, scoring 26 points, grabbing 10 rebounds and dishing five assists, including two full-court passes, in the Nuggets' first preseason game.
